  <brief_title>Customized Titanium Membrane for Growing Jaw Bone Horizontally</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Use of Customized Titanium Membrane for Horizontal Ridge Augmentation With Simultaneous Implant Placement</official_title>
  <sponsors>
