      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Male or female, age &gt;18

          -  Overall good, stable health

          -  A single missing mandibular 1st molar for at least 3 months

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Any medical conditions that may contradict implant and bone surgery or influence the
