          -  Pregnancy or lactating mothers

          -  Current heavy smokers (&gt;10 cigarettes/day) or previous heavy smokers who have quit
             less than one year

          -  Unstable or unsuitable oral conditions for implant and bone surgery (detailed criteria
             in case report form)
      </textblock>
